snippet.title: Cult of the Wind - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Cult of the Wind is a game about people who pretend to be airplanes, and it's finally out of Early Access and into Full Release on STEAM!

Get it here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/293840/
Website: http://www.cultofthewind.com
